{"tid":993642,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬觸傷舊患 杜曹佢對曼聯無法上陣","createTime":"2019-01-24T05:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T12:53:00.000Z","uid":186071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"56cfbba472ccdaa49c062306c398385c7a31e4cc","tid":993642,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:34:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=7jr721pX1FVco0rX7P5j%2BI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=bb1389db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】巴黎聖日耳門證實周三在法足盃傷出的尼馬，觸傷第5蹠骨舊患，會方與尼馬自己同表憂心。<br />\n<br />\nPSG在周三法足盃打敗斯特拉斯堡後發表聲明，證實經過初步診斷，尼馬（Neymar）的第5蹠骨受創令他痛楚，表示會考慮用盡一切方法協助尼馬。這位世界轉會費紀錄保持者去季因同一傷處，而錯過3個月比賽。<br />\n<br />\n「醫生擔憂，尼馬擔憂，因為那是同一條腿，同一位置。」教練杜慈同時批評球證沒好好保護尼馬：「那是他被犯規3次的處境，一次又一次，球證甚麼也沒有做。」<br />\n<br />\n尼馬疑似受傷，令人懷疑他或錯過下月鬥曼聯的歐聯大戰，PSG將在2月13日歐聯16強首回合作客曼聯，3月7日則主場迎戰紅魔。如果尼馬趕不及披甲的話，PSG戰力勢必有所削弱。"},{"pid":"edfef7305f621414d3c99c3d4164f9e709234e4c","tid":993642,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"條撚樣次次驚輸都喺法國踢衛生波受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79dfd528c6af45e194ee96c453a98c8a8bf868e1","tid":993642,"uid":111006,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"edfef7305f621414d3c99c3d4164f9e709234e4c","tid":993642,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"條撚樣次次驚輸都喺法國踢衛生波受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:39:16.000Z","msg":"曼聯都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ebbd29f176b2c82316a1421596053ee73034a5","tid":993642,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"79dfd528c6af45e194ee96c453a98c8a8bf868e1","tid":993642,"uid":111006,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"edfef7305f621414d3c99c3d4164f9e709234e4c","tid":993642,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1